title: 172: Is Thanksgiving Better Without Family? | Ear Biscuits Ep. 172
description:
Dessert karaoke or gas station card games? How would you rather spend your Thanksgiving? Rhett and Link compare how they spent their Thanksgivings this year to determine how they'd prefer to spend the holiday in the future.
